Our Funds







Our experienced asset managers follow the same investment philosophy The Motley Fool has advocated for over 20 years. We strive to offer you a way to invest in what we believe are the globe's best businesses at what we believe are attractive prices. Learn more about our family of funds below.






 Domestic Small-and-Mid-Cap
Great America Fund




Overall rating applies to investor class shares only. Based on risk-adjusted returns, as of 06/30/2017, out of 576 Mid-Cap Growth Funds.

Fund Facts

 Domestic small and mid cap (SMID) equity fund
 Growth at a reasonable price (GARP) investing style
 Seeks long term capital appreciation
 100% domestic investments


Learn More







