Proxy Voting Information




The performance data quoted represents past performance and does not guarantee future results. Current performance may be lower or higher. The investment return and principal of an investment will fluctuate so that shares, when redeemed, may be worth more or less than their original cost. A redemption fee of 2.00% of the then-current value of the shares redeemed is imposed on redemptions of shares made within 90 days of purchase (i.e., the redemption is effective on or before the 90th day following the date of purchase), subject to certain exceptions. The redemption fee is not reflected in the quoted returns. See additional performance information about each fund at these links: Independence Fund, Great America Fund and Emerging Markets Fund.














 





