*Stock Advisor returns updated daily during market hours. David Gardner owns shares of Amazon.com, Netflix, and Starbucks. Tom Gardner owns shares of Netflix and Starbucks. The Motley Fool owns shares of and recommends Amazon.com, Netflix, and Starbucks. The Motley Fool owns shares of shares of Netflix, Tesla, Apple, and Disney. Mark Hulbert named Motley Fool Rule Breakers, Stock Advisor and Inside Value among the top-ranked stock-picking service for June 2008 through June 2013 in the Wall Street Journal. Glassdoor rated The Motley Fool as the #1 Best Small & Medium Companies to Work For in 2014 and 2015.






















